<SYNC Start=1214237><P Class=KRCC>이거 설마 폴터가이스트?
<SYNC Start=1218909><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1220602><P Class=KRCC>언니!
<SYNC Start=1222624><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1225850><P Class=KRCC>다른 애들은?
<SYNC Start=1227953><P Class=KRCC>우이하루?
<SYNC Start=1230130><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1231451><P Class=KRCC>우이하루!
<SYNC Start=1233869><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1246954><P Class=KRCC>사텐, 괜찮아?
<SYNC Start=1249417><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1260766><P Class=KRCC>위기일발이었어
<SYNC Start=1263428><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1264584><P Class=KRCC>다친 덴 없니?
<SYNC Start=1266745><P Class=KRCC>이제 괜찮아
<SYNC Start=1268738><P Class=KRCC>저분은…
<SYNC Start=1271627><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1275655><P Class=KRCC>하루우에 양, 하루우에 양
<SYNC Start=1279048><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1280023><P Class=KRCC>하루우에 양, 괜찮아요?
<SYNC Start=1282883><P Class=KRCC>무리하지 말고
<SYNC Start=1285161><P Class=KRCC>어디야?
<SYNC Start=1287821><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1288212><P Class=KRCC>어디 있어?
<SYNC Start=1291671><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1292950><P Class=KRCC>하루우에 양?
<SYNC Start=1295760><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1306809><P Class=KRCC>- 저기 무너졌어<br>- 무슨 사고 났나?
